Surat’s first art café is finally opening.

Boho’d Art Café opens its doors on July 1st — and you’re invited to experience art like never before.

Pick your seat, choose what you want to make (from pottery to painting to DIY art), and spend a couple of hours off-screen, hands-on, and fully present.

The vibe’s casual, the art is for everyone, and the food? Just enough to keep you fueled.

🪄 You’ll need to pre-book your slot.
📍Booking link is now live in our profile.
Tag your art buddy and grab a table before they fill up!

#BohodArtCafe #ArtOnTheMenu #SuratBuz

You asked for something different, Surat — so here we are.
Boho’d Art Café is opening this July.
A one-of-its-kind walk-in café where you don’t just sip, you create.

From pottery to painting, printing to play — pick your art like you’d pick a latte.
All age groups. No prior booking. No pressure. Just art, flow, and vibes.

💥 We’re opening the doors soon — and trust us, you’ll want in.
Stay tuned.

#BohodArtCafe #SuratArtScene #CreateLikeYouMeanIt #OpeningSoon
